Create a complete React + TailwindCSS accounting dashboard app called "Numeris".

## Stack
- React 18 with Vite
- TailwindCSS v3
- Recharts for charts
- React Router v6 for navigation
- lucide-react for icons

## File structure
src/
  components/
    Sidebar.jsx
    Topbar.jsx
    MetricCard.jsx
    BillsChart.jsx
    DeadlinesList.jsx
    QuickActions.jsx
    InvoicesTable.jsx
  pages/
    Dashboard.jsx
  data/
    mockData.js
  App.jsx
  main.jsx

## Sidebar (dark navy #1a2332)
- Logo: blue rounded square "N" + "Numeris" text
- Nav sections with icons (lucide-react):
  - Dashboard (LayoutDashboard)
  - Clients (Users)
  - FINANCE: Invoices (FileText), Bills (ClipboardList), Payments (CreditCard), Exports (Download)
  - WORK: Projects (FolderOpen), Time Tracking (Clock)
  - REPORTS: Accounting (BookOpen), Reports (BarChart2)
- Active state: blue left border + light blue bg tint
- Bottom: user avatar circle + name
- Collapses to icons only on mobile

## Topbar
- Page title left
- Right: bell icon, help icon, "Upgrade Plan" blue button
- White bg, bottom border

